{
  "texts": [
    "These learned characteristics can be used to establish supervised model weights or to refine subsequent tasks.",
    "Recent research 50 has examined the use of transformer-based architectures for multimodal unsupervised learning from raw video, audio, and text.",
    "Using self-supervised learning techniques, the plan is to implement a transformer-based architecture capable of handling multiple modalities and capable of predicting the next frame, audio, or text given the current one.",
    "Recent efforts have been made to make Vision Transformer models more effective in terms of computation time and memory consumption.",
    "Multiple architectures, such as Separable Vision Transformer (SepViT) 51 and Reversible Vision Transformer (RViT) 37, 52, have been proposed by researchers that are capable of achieving comparable or superior performance than conventional ViT models while being more energy-efficient."
  ]
}